# Phase 1: Analyze the Fix

This is a patch for LoopIdiomVectorize:

[LoopIdiomVectorize] Avoid wrapping in find_first_of loops.
As noted in https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/pull/179298#discussion_r2757948654, use integer induction variables to avoid potential pointer wrap.
